What is LEFT JOIN?
LEFT JOIN left table के सभी records return करता है, चाहे matching record right table में हो या नहीं।

Query
SELECT
c.CustomerID,
c.Name,
o.OrderID
FROM Customers c
LEFT JOIN Orders o
ON c.CustomerID = o.CustomerID

Result
CustomerID	Name	OrderID
1	          John	 101
2	          Sarah	 102
3	          Mike	 NULL
